<plot>Seven year old Manny wants his Mommy close to him at all times, but despite her love for him, she leaves him home alone. Manny has developed a close relationship with his grandparent's spirits, who watch over him. A brief sighting of the grim reaper disturbs Manny even though he's comfortable with the world of the dead.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?252821</url></doc>
